Billing/Allopass version 0.01
=============================


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    HTTP::Request::Common
    LWP::UserAgent
    CGI::Cookie
 

